149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"假设大公爵们依然会采取正面行动，我们还有多少时间？","id":150,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#5$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"如果伊内丝小姐成功......温德米尔公爵的高速军舰会在日出后不久靠近这里。","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"你们在这里聚集了很多人。","id":154,"figure":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_863_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":155},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"贝尔德","text":"那些不在这里的人，应该也已经收到消息了，愿意跟着我们的人会跟上队伍的。","id":156,"figure":"avg_npc_863_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"那我建议在大公爵的军舰正式靠近之前，我们应该继续在这里等待。","id":158,"figure":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"眼下的情况......走在街道上不是个好主意。","id":160,"figure":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"戴菲恩","text":"无论是威灵顿还是开斯特，他们对有可能妨碍他们的人都从不手软。","id":162,"figure":"avg_npc_866_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"不，我们最好现在就出发。","id":164,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"封锁墙边的几个萨卡兹驻军营地被袭击了，很可能就是某位大公爵的部队干的。","id":165,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"我们应该趁着现在还是夜里，尽量靠近那些封锁墙防守比较薄弱的地带。","id":166,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":167},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"更重要的是......我们要让还躲在窗户后面张望的那些人知道，我们说的是真的。","id":168,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"这次撤离不是个为了骗取他们仅剩储备的阴谋，不是个萨卡兹剿灭他们的陷阱。","id":169,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"重新建立信任是困难的，而唯一的方法不过是——","id":170,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1","focus":"m","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"推进之王","text":"让他们看见实际的行动。","id":172,"figure":"avgnew_112_siege_1#12$1"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":173},{"type":"Dialog","id":174},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":175},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":176},{"type":"Background","image":"21_G1_interrogat_room","screenadapt":"coverall","id":177},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":179},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"$darkness02_loop","volume":"0.6","id":180,"musicid":2},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"......","id":182,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"喏，这几本是你上次托我带的书。","id":184,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"我可在那些伦蒂尼姆的图书馆里找了半天，我又不懂维多利亚语，最后是抓了个可怜的菲林才帮你找到。","id":186,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"谢谢。","id":188,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"我看你有时还会在另一个空白的本子上写写画画。","id":190,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"你不光看书，还会自己写东西？","id":192,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"我没去过卡兹戴尔，但听说那里的地窖里甚至还有间萨卡兹的大学。","id":194,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"你是那里的老师？","id":196,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_393_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"不，我和你一样，为人卖命。","id":198,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"这些书真的这么好看？","id":200,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_393_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"都是些差不多的结论，只是相似的情形一遍遍上演。","id":202,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_393_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"作者们就只能继续得出这些差不多的结论。","id":204,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_393_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"我同样觉得腻烦。","id":206,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#7$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"曼弗雷德将军让我们把你关在这里，却一直没有进一步的指令......","id":208,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"你是怎么得罪他了？","id":210,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_393_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":211},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"或许，他只是觉得，对于我来说，监狱更安静。","id":212,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_393_1#2$1","focus":"m","id":213},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"在这里......更方便我做些真正愿意去做的事。","id":214,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#2$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":215},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"你真正愿意去做的事情就是看书？","id":216,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"那你可真够无聊的。","id":218,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"听说......咱们萨卡兹很快就要有个真正的好消息了。","id":220,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"能够震撼整片大地的好消息！","id":222,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"无非是又一场战争。","id":224,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"有没有人和你说过，跟你聊天很没劲？","id":226,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_393_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":227},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"赫德雷","text":"倒是真有。","id":228,"figure":"avg_npc_393_1#3$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":229},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"......更没劲了。","id":230,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"好了，我要换班了。你老实在这里待着吧。","id":232,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"别忘了答应我的，帮你找书的报酬——","id":234,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":235},{"type":"charslot","id":236},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":237},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":238},{"type":"Text","text":"王庭军士兵的身影晃晃悠悠地消失在监狱走廊的尽头，很快，另一串脚步声就会响起。","id":239},{"type":"Text","text":"赫德雷等待着。","id":240},{"type":"Text","text":"但是只有寂静。","id":241},{"type":"Dialog","id":242},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":243},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":244},{"type":"Background","image":"37_g9_airshipdockcorridor","screenadapt":"coverall","id":245},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":246},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":247},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_404_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"曼弗雷德","text":"......","id":249,"figure":"avg_npc_404_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"王庭军士兵","text":"船员们都已经登上飞空艇了。","id":251,"figure":"avg_npc_419_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_404_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"曼弗雷德","text":"我知道了。","id":253,"figure":"avg_npc_404_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_404_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":254},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"曼弗雷德","text":"明椒。","id":255,"figure":"avg_npc_404_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"呃......我在！","id":257,"figure":"avg_4071_peper_1#8$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_404_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"曼弗雷德","text":"你看过一本......叫《萨卡兹战争史》的书吗？","id":259,"figure":"avg_npc_404_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"......没有。","id":261,"figure":"avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_404_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"曼弗雷德","text":"你该看看，我的抽屉里有一本，你可以拿去。","id":263,"figure":"avg_npc_404_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#11$1","focus":"m","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"那是个很精彩的故事吗？","id":265,"figure":"avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_404_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":266},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"曼弗雷德","text":"那是一本战争史。","id":267,"figure":"avg_npc_404_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#14$1","focus":"m","id":268},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"您已经说了......","id":269,"figure":"avg_4071_peper_1#14$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_404_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":270},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"曼弗雷德","text":"那你就不该问这样的问题。","id":271,"figure":"avg_npc_404_1#6$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_404_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":272},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"曼弗雷德","text":"我不认同这本书中的几乎一切观点，软弱，悲哀，破碎。","id":273,"figure":"avg_npc_404_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_404_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"曼弗雷德","text":"但我仍然承认，那是本浸透着鲜血的书。","id":275,"figure":"avg_npc_404_1#1$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4071_peper_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"明椒","text":"那位作者又会怎么描述我们眼下的这场战争呢？","id":277,"figure":"avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_404_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"曼弗雷德","text":"......","id":279,"figure":"avg_npc_404_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"曼弗雷德","text":"我同样好奇。","id":280,"figure":"avg_npc_404_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":281},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":282},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":283},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":284},{"type":"Character","id":285},{"type":"Image","id":286}],"characters":["阿米娅","“灰礼帽”","贝尔德","推进之王","戴菲恩","卡铎尔","赫德雷","王庭军士兵","曼弗雷德","明椒"]}